display_long_description:
Create complexly colorful **domino reactions** in mixed-reality, and try new features out with consistent **monthly updates**. Place, curve, and build amazing domino creations while channeling your inner domino artist.✨

[media]

# NEW February '25 Update: Personalized Color Update
You can now choose the colors for your individual dominos, enabling greater creativity!

[media]

# Key Features
- Place, curve, and build domino reactions
- Your creations are saved over multiple sessions
- Choose from vibrant domino colors

# Tips
Pinch with your hands facing down to create dominos, and turn your palm up to access your reset button and in-game menu! 

# You're Amazing
We are so thankful for our early access supporters! Don't forget to join our discord here to be a part of the Domino World community: https://discord.com/invite/xAX9hJZSzM
